column5: Leslie Neilsen died of complications from pnemonia yesterday.  RIP Leslie Nielsen

One of my all time favs... I just look at him and I would start to laugh... "Nice beaver" "Thanks, I just had it stuffed yesterday" "Have you ever been to a turkish prison Billy?" May he rest in peace, with a smile on his face combined with a look of complete confusion. HH
One of my all time fav  hey look it's enrico pallazzo!!!
AMEN BRO. One of the funniest people i have ever seen.He started out his carrer as a dramtic actor, but his directors couldnt keep a straight face between takes.
There's a small inflation nozzle.. just below the belt line..
Doing nothing is very hard to do...you never know when you're finished

“You're excited? You should feel my nipples!”  ---------------------------------------- Your dog sure has a surprised look on his face. That's because you're looking at his butt. Uh, then he's certainly not going to enjoy that treat I just fed to him. -------------------------------------------- You'd better tell the captain we've got to land as soon as we can. This woman has to be gotten to a hospital. A hospital? What is it? It's a big building with patients, but that's not important right now.  ------------------- The life of everyone on board depends upon just one thing: finding someone back there who can not only fly this plane, but who didn't have fish for dinner.  ---------- Leslie will be missed by many but will continue to make us laugh for years to come.  Randy

He was funny alright but I always thought his brother Erik was funnier.
At least Erik got an airport named after him!
Great comedic actor.  My favorite line was when Precilla Presley was sucking on his finger and he said "I've got nine more".  I actually used that line on a girlfriend once, it was classic.  RIP.
And don't call me Shirley....man he was awesome
